76 pages of Astounding Action-Packed Arachnid-Adventure! Only £3.50!Astonishing Spider-Man Vol.5 #27

Spiral continues! Has Wraith finally crossed the line from hero to villain?! Can Spidey and his ally stop the Circus of Crime?!

Also, Spider-Gwen faces some harsh truths about the death of Peter Parker – and her part in it!

Plus, Spider-Ham versus the Swinester Six! (Yes, we know swinester isn’t a real word.)

By Gerry Conway, Carlo Barberi, Jason Latour, Robbi Rodriguez, Tom DeFalco and Jacob Chabot!

Includes material reprinted from Amazing Spider-Man #19.1, Spider-Gwen #4 and Spider-Ham 25th Anniversary Special #1.
Contains episode 96 - 99.

description:
This anthology is all about exhibitionism! A detective must perform sexual acts in public to uncover the location of a bomb, a soldier performs for the enemy to save the lives of her men and citizens, and a bartending hostess puts on a show for a regular's birthday. All that and more, in this collection of seven “totally exposed” shorts from different creators.

Story Titles

  • The Exposed Sexy Body by Parfait
  • Exhibitionist Knight Chris by Daisuke Segami
  • The Enslaved Idol by Rumi Matsunami
  • Afterschool Exposure by Umekichi
  • The Self-Conscious Boy, Black Magic, and I by Maki
  • A Barren Flower in the War: Operation Decoy by Take
  • Girlsbar: Pink Pompadour by Nishiki Karasuma
name: Vol. 1

description: Old and new dangers coalesce as Fale and Del make their way through the Delphion Gate; the shattered mouth that leads into the diseased gut of Zone 1, where some 'thing' will bar their way to freedom.
name: Vol. 2

description:
NOTE: This version has language appropriate for younger readers.

Things have changed for Bridget since her fight with the Cailleach, and they're gonna change for all of us now...

volume.name: The Ballad of Brighid of Atlanta

description: In Issue #7, Stuart learns more things about Bonnie, Mimi dips her toe into casual dating, and Herb reveals his human side.
name: Book Seven

volume.name: Bonnie N. Collide, Nine to Five

description:
Ervin, once the pride and joy of the science world, comes of age as he finds himself exposed to the harsh realities of life.

Dismembered and smuggled out of England by a mysterious character called The Alchemist, Ervin finally experiences the one thing he has longed for - to be human, and he quickly realises that the world outside Hodgson's Brewery gates is a cruel place.

This book is the final part of the Tick Tock IPA trilogy. It's a story of how a Clockwork Servant became sentient, a development that shook the moral fabric of British Society, Industry, the Church, and the Crown.
name: Tick Tock IPA 3

description:
Exit

Alex Cooper falls into the dream world of Comatose, a world that is part dream, part game; full of action, adventure, and blood thirsty monsters. With the help of his friend Kevin he begins to make his escape from this world, but they soon discover that there is more to this world than meets the eye. Follow Kevin and Alex and their adventures in Comatose.

Chapter 3: Exit

Kevin encounters an old "friend" while he and Alex continue to make their escape from Comatose. Alex has an idea of how he might escape immediately.
name: Exit

description: Crystal collects the first of the Spirit Knight Jewels and learns some of the basics about using magic. The evil sorceress moves in next door.

Spiffie and Beyond!

When Bob's hometown is invaded by an insane alien,-- The Disgruntled Avenger must take action! With the help his apartment's maintenance man. (Bon Zoffo Ba-zon) Bob will go where no man has gone before! But,-- The aliens have an ace up their sleeves... The super villain 'Mr. Happy!'
name: Spiffie and Beyond!

description: Doug and Sophie continue their love/hate relationship in another year's worth of the syndicated comic strip "Dog eat Doug".
name: At the Mountains of Mucus

description:
Battle 06

Morris meets with Mia's father to discuss their mutual enemy while Raid and June plot to take their master's fortune.
name: Battle 6

description: I Love You, You Big Weirdo compiles the second two years of Finn and Charlie are Hitched, a webcomic telling the story of a married gay couple, their friends, and their adventures in domesticity.
name: I Love You, You Big Weirdo

description:
Corruption Pt. 2

With the powerful police bots corrupted and on the loose, the Lightspeed Enforcers have been sent out to the streets in attempt to put them down. Can they slow down these deadly weapons?
name: Corruption Pt. 2

description:
Predator!

Lou and the crew respond to a distress call from a stricken space station, only to find the monster on-board is not all it seems....
name: Predator!

description:
The noise of thunder, part nine.

The first story arc approaches its end as more detail about Tessa Theus and the world of Manifest are unveiled.
name: The Noise of Thunder, Part Nine

description:
Featuring screen-capture images from MARVEL'S ULTIMATE SPIDER-MAN: WEB WARRIORS. Explosive action from your favorite web-slinging wonder, based on the hit Disney XD animated series! Spider-Man gets to roll with the big boys as Captain America and Wolverine join him to combat a dangerous new threat to S.H.I.E.L.D.! Then, Spidey must team up with Norman Osborn, now piloting the Iron Patriot Armor! Osborn swears he's put his villainous past behind him, but can Spidey trust his former foe? When Dracula attacks, Spider-Man teams up with Blade — but can even these two heroes defeat the King of the Vampires? Spidey might just need a little help from his friends — the secret team of monster heroes known as the Howling Commandos!

Collects Marvel Universe Ultimate Spider-Man: Web Warriors #9-12.
name: Volume 3

description:
Electrolyte Rising!!!

Electrolyte's powers go haywire as he grows to Godzilla-size. He makes short work of Conniption and Honey Badger but destroys the city's marina in the process. The Mayor of Megalopolis forces Electrolyte to repay his debt to the city by finding the evil mastermind, ThinkTank.
name: Electrolyte Rising!!!

volume.name: The Misadventures of Electrolyte and The Justice Purveyors

description: The Sixsmiths are a family of suburban Satanists recoving from the global recession. Their eldest daughter, Jezabelle, has returned to the fold with a frightening amount of zeal. Meanwhile, recently converted Dennis O'Dowell finds that adopting a new faith has not made him as cool as he had hoped. But when the church bruns down the whole community is embroiled in a crisis. What hidden enemy has brought them this low? Or is the Dark Lord punishing them for their weakness? Collects issues 1-3. Its The Simpsons meets Teh Osbournes.
name: Volume Two

description:
It's a party, but who the hell brought this grass?!

SOD #3

Well, what do you know? In issue #3 of SOD, JB has gone and saved Sod City from certain despair . . . but at what cost? Sure, the grass is finally greener on THIS side of the fence and the town is enjoying an upswing, but PEOPLE ARE VANISHING!!! And in other news, JB's pretty young bride just might have a thing for our local comic‐ book‐writing nerd of a misfit known as Rift! All the drama comes to pass at a town party ‐‐ the biggest shindig Sod City has ever put on! And, unbeknownst to all, the proverbial shit is about to hit the fan. Yup, there's gonna be some killer grass at this party . . . and we don't mean weed. We mean KILLER GRASS!

Dig into SOD #3 today!
Encased in a hopeless situation, Toby takes a desperate decision.

The Dynamic Five

Five strange visitors arrive in the town of Waverly, New York, sending them on a collision course with Ulysses the Polar Bear. Featuring guest writer Tom Peyer (BATMAN '66, HOURMAN).
name: Chapter 4: The Dynamic Five

description:
Virgin's Blood Pt.1

Virgin nurses Hania's injuries while the Cleric takes the fight to the town of Le'Saint seeking to lure Virgin out of hiding.
name: Virgin's Blood Pt.1

description:
In "Berserker", Melissa interviews the kids behind the creation of the LGBTQ club for her first article for the school newspaper. Meanwhile, Casey goes for a neighborhood walk that has some unexpected surprises, both good and bad.

In "The Good Child", Yoshiko finally goes on her honeymoon trip to Europe. With her mysterious new friend Lynette, she becomes involved in an incident of life and death that has nothing to do with her own family, for a change.
name: Berserker; The Good Child

description:
Norman is a BIG yeti with a SMALL problem.

He doesn't know who - or what - he is.

All alone in the Arctic snows, there's no one to ask, so Norman does what any lonely, confused young yeti would do: he sets off on a quest to find out for himself. Along the way, he meets many strange creatures - talking trees, tea-loving wolves, and a particularly pinchy crab but none of them have the answer he seeks.

Will Norman ever find out who he is?

Or will the men hunting a monster find him first?

Follow Norman on an epic journey of discovery to answer the ultimate question of questions:

WHO AM I?
name: Who Am I?

description:
Cat Squad Alpha

Ace Purrwalker is sent on the search for an unfaithful individual inside Cat Squad Alpha. Luke is having a bad day, while his nerd friend Leeloo makes a shocking discovery.
name: Cat Squad Alpha

description:
A Preamble of Power: Part I

What if America had never been a democracy but a monarchy? It's modern day America but under the rule and reign of a descendant of George Washington, Prince Geoffrey.
name: A Preamble of Power: Part I

description:
Detective Renee Scharf has solved some of the most disturbing and violent cases the city of Infinity Hill has ever seen. But nothing she's witnessed before could have prepared her for what's coming next.

As she's about to find out, sometimes the right person to fear is the one you're supposed to love the most.

In a world ripped apart by Paradox, haunted by memories of his fading histories but armed with new math and machines provided by the prevailing futures, Floyd Solar races to save the last remnants of humanity, who dwell within the Zero Block, and to reunite with his one true love.

Web Head - A shy little fellow from the suburbs is in love with a beautiful red headed girl. When some bullies from the neighborhood torment his beloved, one he finds a courage within he never imagined he could have.

The Submarine Boy - A boy is mocked by his classmates because of his big ears, but an accident during a swimming competition will change how the other children see him.

Tin Face - A little boy suffers bullying in school due to his physical disability, but one day he uses his wits to create an incredible super armor to defend himself and his best friend.
name: Web Head; The Submarine Boy; Tin Face

description:
Dare you brave the hellish arena that provides the ultimate in adrenaline-fueled entertainment on Battleworld — Arcade's Killiseum? It's the scorching-hot track where cursed souls race at the speed of sin, everything goes, and the only rule is: don't even think there are any rules! As Ghost Riders both fiendishly familiar and blazingly bizarre go skull-to-flaming-skull, first is first and anywhere else is nowhere. Robbie Reyes, Johnny Blaze, Dan Ketch, Carter Slade, Alejandra Blaze and Zero Cochrane assemble on the starting line! Choose your favorite, and watch them go to war! But on this track of treachery, can anyone truly emerge victorious? Plus: Johnny faces a classic Deathrace! And will Robbie Reyes fall in love with Ms. Marvel herself, Kamala Khan?

Collects Ghost Racers #1-4, Secret Wars: Secret Love #1 (7 page story), Ghost Rider (1973) #35.
name: TPB

description:
In a time of quiet peace, a remnant from a Knightly order lingers on; not to protect the people of the world from injustice, but to simply maintain their old guard.

The order of the Knights of the Black Star have buried themselves away from the common people, never aware of the dangers that lurk from beyond their gaze. Outside dangers lurk that only know death and crave bloodied townspeople!

Hunter's Lore follows a single member of this faction, Rowan Black. Growing restless with his seclusion, Rowan abandons his duties in search of redemption and glory through the quests laid before him, of the people who desperately need a hero. During the journey he fights to become more than simply a Knight of the Black Star.

As a little boy, Jade was so fascinated by the folk tales grandpa told him--mysterious creatures and big monsters living in the land of shadow... But now he find himself being dragged into the land of shadow, and all the things in grandpa's stories become real! With the help of shadow creatures, Jade has to fight the big monster from devouring the moon...And he eventually gains the courage to say farewell to his beloved grandfather.

Who Owns the Sky #1

Jack and WeFlyHi are getting ready to meet, greet and check out their rivals in the sky at the annual skymixer. See what happens when new rivals try to play nice...
name: Who Owns the Sky #1

description:
Spare

Jumbe finds himself delivering a package to a frog like alien robot race. The thing is, they seem to be more interested in Jumbe than the package.
name: Spare

description:
The Knight Hunter

It all begins here! This is the first issue of the Knight Hunter series. Trent Walker is kidnapped and brought to a strange facility in a high octane first issue!

When the lights go out, a young boy is faced with his worst fears.

This comic was started on 10/3/2015 at 10:00 AM as part of 24-Hour Comic Day. It was completed on 10/4/2015 at 8:47 AM.

When Masatsugu's father spontaneously decides to travel the world, Masatsugu is forced into the role of company president. The plus side is that the secretary assigned to him is Shiroba, the man he's madly in love with. But Shiroba only seems to see Masatsugu as his boss instead of as a potential lover. If Masatsugu pulls a few strings, he can win Shiroba's body. However, Masatsugu isn't quite as in charge as he thinks he is.

Obey Your Secretary! features three short stories of strong and confident secretaries who use unconventional (and sexy) methods to whip their bosses into shape. Also included are two stories of sweet office romance. It's not always a bad idea to get your meat where you make your bread!

Contents

  • Obey Your Secretary! Scene. 1: My Bonus Is Your Body
  • Obey Your Secretary! Scene. 2: A Sadistic Secretary Educates His Hopeless Boss
  • Obey Your Secretary! Scene. 3: My Revenge Includes You
  • It Must Be Love
  • Fall In Love the Second Time Around
name: Vol. 1

description:
Don't Think Twice, It's All Right

Andrew's family has always been close to death, just not in the way most people think. It's a typical night in a typically terrible part of town. Waiting in the rain, Andrew watches as a young couple exits a nightclub to seek shelter from a near-by bus stop. They thought they were safe, this couldn't be further from the truth. Three local ruffians who followed this young couple are out for blood, and they just so happened to find it. Andrew reluctantly sit's back and watches the carnage unfold till he just can't take it anymore. Andrew needs to do something, and luckily he has the power.
name: Don't Think Twice, It's All Right

description:
A small collection of short stories featuring important moments in the lives of Gwen, Nate & Nick.

It's a good starting point for new readers and a thank you note to old fans.

Oh, and it's funny too!
The series launches with a tribute to the fantasy artist Harry Roland (d. 2009), reprinting Kendar the Jungle Lord and Blood & Gold in their original format for the first time since 2006.
Chris had heard tales of mysterious ape-like creatures his entire life, but never gave them much thought...until the night he came face-to-face with the Spawn of the Sasquatch!

The Birth of a Speedster

Have you ever wondered what it would be like to wake up and be more than you ever were?

Welcome to the world of SPEEDSTAR. When a mysterious meteorite crashes down practically in their backyard, a group of friends do only the most sensible thing: touch it of course! A devastating accident occurs and friends are lost, but when Ben Grant begins to develop astonishing new abilities, his world is turned on its head!

Join us as he discovers his new abilities and becomes the hero known to the world as SPEEDSTAR!
name: The Birth of A Speedster

description:
Starting Point!

After a humiliating rescue by a super-hero on live TV, 300 pound single mom Renee Garcia-Gibson agrees to try an experimental diet drug to reduce her outward appearance. But the change to her metabolism comes with the unexpected side-effect of giving her super-speed! Moments after her transformation, Renee must use her amazing new powers to tackle the mob muscle-man known as Glut as well as a nefarious anti-hero army called The Cloud! Veteran TV comedy writer Darin Henry (Seinfeld, Futurama, KC Undercover) joins forces with artist extraordinaire Craig Rousseau (Batman Beyond, Harley Quinn) to bring you the awesome origin of Startup, the newest star in the Sitcomics galaxy of heroes!
name: Starting Point!

description: Kassem learns his secret business, butchering and selling human flesh, is comprimised when a stranger blackmails him in to acquiring the "meat" of a particular person. The logistics and the morality involved in completing the job are surprisingly problematic though.
Reporter Benjamin Morris begins to have nightmares that slowly erode his life, while two investigators attempt to unravel the reality and consequences surrounding these dreams.

When a race of super powerful zombies called Metrids start to reappear after fifteen years, John "Doc Synapse" Harrison must reassamble the team that stopped them the first time. Only the team isn't answering the call.

Eric Martin - Vengador Now the city of Sydney has a new protector watching over it.

After a traumatic even occurs in the Martin family, Eric's world is turned upside down as he realizes how corruption is plaguing the city.

He realizes that the only way for justice to be served is to take matters into his own hands. How far will Vengador go to ensure that justice prevails

Can one man make a difference in a world that is full of corruption?
name: Vol. 1

volume.name: Vengador: There Is No Such Thing As Justice

description:
The Woman With The Dead Eyes

Josiah Black has been many things, from outlaw to sheriff and from husband to widower. Now a hired gun he takes on the task to kill the murderer of the beautiful Greta Anderson's family. However, things are never as straight forward as they at first appear and he sets off never suspecting that soon he will be adding 'monster hunter' to his list.
name: The Woman With The Dead Eyes

description: Hilarious sex humor within! Seen in independent publications nationwide, Sonya Samantha Saturday's "Load" is the one comic strip unafraid to laugh at the most intimate parts human nature. This full-color collection contains over 70 of the best strips from 2006 to 2008, ten in color for the first time. The book also contains the one page comic "The Morning F*****r's Guide to Morning Love", not available anywhere else!

volume.name: Why Do You Cry When I'm On Top?

description: Ephelia begins her journey on a rough patch. Though she has escaped the castle that has kept her trapped, things get more intense than she anticipated while running away from soldiers.
name: Vol. 1

description:
The Witch Book

Easy-to-read comic. Ages: 6-8, grade 1-3.

There are two kinds of witches:

Black witches, who are bad and white witches, who are good.

---

Mia has just lost her grandmother.

A golden bracelet is her only keepsake from her.

The bad girl, Olga, steals it.

Mia gets mad and wants revenge.

She finds out that she has the powers of a witch.

But will she choose to be a black witch or a white witch?
name: Volume 1

description:
The original Age of Apocalypse saga comes to an explosive end as the alternate-universe X-Men's desperate gambles bear fruit! Gambit recovers the artifact that might end Apocalypse's reign before it began, while Weapon X obtains the means to destroy his kingdom — and Generation Next pays the ultimate price rescuing Illyana Rasputin! But even armed with all the pieces to their puzzle, can the X-Men and their allies storm Apocalypse's stronghold, rescue Magneto, pull off their plan and restore the original Marvel Universe? Who will live? Who will die? And who will escape the destruction of the Age of Apocalypse?

Collects Weapon X (1995) #3-4, Generation Next #3-4, Gambit and the X-Ternals #3-4, Astonishing X-Men (1995) #4, X-Man #4, X-Calibre #4, Factor X #4, Amazing X-Men (1995) #4, X-Universe #2, X-Men Omega, Age of Apocalypse: The Chosen.
name: Volume 3
